name: ChartBinOptions
description: Encapsulates the bon options only for histogram chart and pareto chart.

properties.name: type
properties.description: Returns or sets bin type of a histogram chart or pareto chart. ReadWrite.

properties.name: count
properties.description: Returns or sets count of bin of a histogram chart or pareto chart. ReadWrite.

properties.name: allowOverflow
properties.description: Returns or sets if bin overflow enabled in a histogram chart or pareto chart. ReadWrite.

properties.name: allowUnderflow
properties.description: Returns or sets if bin underflow enabled in a histogram chart or pareto chart. ReadWrite.

properties.name: width
properties.description: Returns or sets bin width value of a histogram chart or pareto chart. ReadWrite.

properties.name: overflowValue
properties.description: Returns or sets bin overflow value of a histogram chart or pareto chart. ReadWrite.

properties.name: underflowValue
properties.description: Returns or sets bin underflow value of a histogram chart or pareto chart. ReadWrite.
